.TH mtvtoppm 1 "02 February 1989"
.SH NAME
mtvtoppm - convert output from Mark VanDeWettering's ray tracer into a portable pixmap
.SH SYNOPSIS
mtvtoppm [mtvfile]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Reads an mtv file as input.
Produces a portable pixmap as output.
